summary:
Here's me bragging a little bit: 
I like to think of myself as a pretty social person and an open, effective communicator. Part of it is that I'm empathic, I really feel what others feel.

I enjoy explaining math to others. I used to be a programmer but I don't want to do technical stuff in my own brain space in front of a computer all day long. I mostly spend my free time with friends and family. I like long, stupid conversations that don't go anywhere. I like people and I don't care for politics. Otherwise I play video games, read books, watch movies, sometimes I'll go to a museum, that kind of thing.
